  "text": "All these data suggest that telomerase activity plays a wider role in maintaining cellular and biological functions than just merely telomere maintenance. These functions are highly relevant to the potential use of 'telomerized tissues' in tissue engineering and include anti-apoptotic effects, effects on differentiated cellular functions, genomic stability and DNA repair. These novel functions for telomerase have been termed 'extracurricular activities' [CITATION_1] .",
